00:39:44.859 --> 00:39:45.859
&gt;&gt;Male #5: What's the worst beer you've ever
had and [inaudible].

00:39:45.859 --> 00:39:46.859
&gt;&gt;Greg: The worst beer that we've ever produced?

00:39:46.859 --> 00:39:47.859
&gt;&gt;Male #5: No, no, no.

00:39:47.859 --> 00:39:49.640
&gt;&gt;Greg: That I've ever tasted.

00:39:49.640 --> 00:39:52.090
[laughter] The worst beer that I've ever
tasted.

00:39:52.090 --> 00:39:57.030
Unfortunately, I have to say that that's near
countless.

00:39:57.030 --> 00:40:02.240
But fortunately, not as countless as all
these incredible beers that I have also gotten

00:40:02.240 --> 00:40:03.290
to taste.

00:40:03.290 --> 00:40:06.390
I am not on the side of the fence that says
there's no

00:40:06.390 --> 00:40:07.640
such thing as a bad beer.

00:40:07.640 --> 00:40:09.390
I can
tell you, I'm in the industry, there's lots

00:40:09.390 --> 00:40:11.410
of really bad beer out there.

00:40:11.410 --> 00:40:14.720
But
fortunately, today -- this is what's so wonderful

00:40:14.720 --> 00:40:17.859
about
all this, there's more great beer than bad

00:40:17.859 --> 00:40:20.369
beer out there
by a wide margin.

00:40:20.369 --> 00:40:23.380
And the great beer out there is really
great.

00:40:23.380 --> 00:40:26.640
So, I'm not going to name a particular brand
name.

00:40:26.640 --> 00:40:29.020
But here's a challenge.

00:40:29.020 --> 00:40:33.520
So much of the bad beer never
intended to be great.

00:40:33.520 --> 00:40:37.420
They intended to fill a market --
what they consider to be a market need or

00:40:37.420 --> 00:40:39.420
market niche or
market opportunity.

00:40:39.420 --> 00:40:43.980
Essentially selling lowest common
denominator stuff to the masses.

00:40:43.980 --> 00:40:48.200
So there was -- it's
not fair to point at it and say, "this is

00:40:48.200 --> 00:40:51.789
a bad beer
because the brew master or somebody, an insider,

00:40:51.789 --> 00:40:54.349
would tell you
under their breath, it was never intended

00:40:54.349 --> 00:40:56.200
to be good.

00:40:56.200 --> 00:40:58.869
It
was never intended to be great.

00:40:58.869 --> 00:40:59.869
Yeah.

